      <ThreadGroup guiclass="ThreadGroupGui" testclass="ThreadGroup" testname="TG_POST_Create_Post">
        <stringProp name="TestPlan.comments">This thread group evaluates the systemâ€™s performance in handling data creation via the /posts endpoint. It uses CSV-based dynamic test data to simulate new post submissions by users. Key metrics include request success rate, average response time, and resource handling under load.

Test Scenario:
1. 10 users will concurrently hit the endpoint within a total runtime of 1 minute.
2. Each user submitting all post data from a CSV file (title, body, userId).
3. Assertions:
    - Response time must be under 5000 ms or mark the request as failed.
    - Assert response code equals 201, as it represents a successful HTTP POST operation.</stringProp>
        <intProp name="ThreadGroup.num_threads">10</intProp>
        <intProp name="ThreadGroup.ramp_time">10</intProp>
        <longProp name="ThreadGroup.duration">60</longProp>
        <longProp name="ThreadGroup.delay">0</longProp>
